body_html:
Thanks
But I figured out the issue..
I am trying to use TensorFlow Libraries in android ndk.
If I place libraries of both 'arm64-v8a' and 'armeabiv-7a' libraries in my project , it works fine. If I remove either of these the above error is thrown.
